<title type="html"><![CDATA[04/13  Is it humanitarianism to keep animals in zoos / Free topics (Host : Maggie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=717&amp;p=745#p745"><![CDATA[
We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br /><br />**** NEW*** Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30 Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00 discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05 Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30 discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00 Individual Presentation <span style="color: #BF0000">(we will be divided into two groups,<br />each person will have two minutes to give a presentation on any topic of that day.)</span><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Sect.1 <br />Do you think is it humanitarianism to keep animals in zoos ?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/aQDYxTCIVRE">https://youtu.be/aQDYxTCIVRE</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Do you think is it humanitarianism to keep animals in zoos ?<br />2. We like to know more about animals, want to see how they look, how they move, so we keep animals in captivity and lock them up, do you think animals like that ?<br />3.African baboon  is dead, and we're sad, but what about other animals? Are they happy? Are they willing to live in a small space?<br />4.What can we do to help animals without suffering from captivity. ?<br />5.What kind of animals are your favorites ?<br /><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 2</span><br />Free topics: <br /><br />1. Introduced yourself (including your family, your work, or interesting ).<br />2. Do you plan go on a trip to somewhere in the future ?( this  coming year )<br />3. Do you think the economy will get better or worse in 2023 ?why ? tell us your opinion.<br />4. Are you content with your situation in the current moment ? if it's not, why ?<br />5. Introduce Taipei city sceneries to outsiders ?For instance :a foreign friend who came from an other country.<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Sun Apr 09, 2023 9:58 am</p><hr />
